about.summary: An importer and exporter for MBTiles

name: mbutil
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "mbutil" %}
{% set version = "0.3.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 78fca26f2497c4e20592792e2fe4abd5fd51e58a03a023a42a54274b7c13c419

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - mbutil

about:
  home: https://github.com/mapbox/mbutil
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: An importer and exporter for MBTiles
  dev_url: https://github.com/mapbox/mbutil

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rluria14
    - oblute
    - benhuff
